loom Joins Action Thriller 'Smart Chase: Fire & Earth,' Partners With Bliss Media On New Production Vehicle (EXCLUSIVE)|first= Elsa|last= Keslassy|date= 16 June 2016|accessdate= 18 June 2016|work= [[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160618145647/https://variety.com/2016/film/news/orlando-bloom-smart-chase-fire-and-earth-1201796951/|archive-date= 18 June 2016|url-status= live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=S.M.A.R.T. Chase new movie poster released|url=http://weibo.com/5866419168/Eyxcm5nUI|website=S.M.A.R.T. Chase at Sina Weibo|publisher=Bliss Media|accessdate=6 March 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190328220825/https://www.weibo.com/5866419168/Eyxcm5nUI|archive-date=28 March 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Barlow|first1=Eve|title=Orlando Bloom on Miranda Kerr, Katy Perry and The Time He Paddleboarded with His Penis Out|url=http://www.elleuk.com/life-and-culture/culture/longform/a35154/orlando-bloom-interview/|website=Elle UK|accessdate=2 May 2017|date=2017-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170502123411/http://www.elleuk.com/life-and-culture/culture/longform/a35154/orlando-bloom-interview/|archive-date=2 May 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| Danny Stratton<ref>{{cite web|last1=Evry|first1=Max|title=Orlando Bloom to Star in Chinese Thriller S.M.A.R.T. Chase: Fire & Earth|url=https://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/696351-orlando-bloom-to-star-in-chinese-thriller-s-m-a-r-t-chase-fire-earth|website=Comingsoon.net|accessdate=20 March 2017|date=2016-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170320234158/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/696351-orlando-bloom-to-star-in-chinese-thriller-s-m-a-r-t-chase-fire-earth|archive-date=20 March 2017|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Tampubolon|first1=Rama|title=Look At Orlando Bloom In This First Image Of Charles Martin's S.M.A.R.T. CHASE|url=http://www.ramascreen.com/look-at-orlando-bloom-in-this-first-image-of-charles-martins-s-m-a-r-t-chase/|website=Rama's Screen|accessdate=20 March 2017|date=2016-11-03}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[The Outpost (2019 film)|The Outpost]]''\n| 1st Lieutenant Benjamin D. Keating\n| Post-production\n|-\n| TBA\n| ''[[Needle in a Timestack]]''\n| \n| Post-production\n|}\n\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| 1994\u201396\n| ''[[Casualty (TV series)|Casualty]]''\n| Noel Harrison\n| Episodes: \"Care in the Community\", \"Another Day in Paradise\", \"Made in Britain\"\n|-\n| 2000\n| ''[[Midsomer Murders]]''\n| Peter Drinkwater\n| Episode: \"Judgement Day\"\n|-\n| 2006\n| ''[[Extras (TV series)|Extras]]''\n| Himself\n| Episode: \"Orlando Bloom\"\n|-\n|2011\n| ''[[Los Angeles Philharmonic|LA Phil Live]]''\n| Romeo\n| Episode: \"Dudamel Conducts Tchaikovsky\"\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[Easy (TV series)|Easy]]''\n| Tom \n| Episode: \"Utopia\"\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2017\n| ''[[Tour de Pharmacy]]''\n| Juju Peppi\n| Television film\n|-\n| ''[[Stairway to Stardom]]''\n| Himself\n| 1 episode\n|-\n| 2019\u2013present\n| ''[[Carnival Row]]''\n| Rycroft Philostrate\n| <ref>{{cite web|last1=Andreeva|first1=Nellie|title=Orlando Bloom To Star In 'Carnival Row' Fantasy Drama Series For Amazon|url=https://deadline.com/2017/08/orlando-bloom-cast-carnival-row-amazon-fantasy-drama-series-1202156081/|website=Deadline Hollywood|accessdate=15 December 2017|date=25 August 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171216091413/http://deadline.com/2017/08/orlando-bloom-cast-carnival-row-amazon-fantasy-drama-series-1202156081/|archive-date=16 December 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Video games===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Voice role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| 2002\n| ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers (video game)|The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers]]''\n| rowspan=\"6\" | Legolas\n| rowspan=\"7\" | Archive sound\n|-\n| 2003\n| ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The