 game)|The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers]]''\n| rowspan=\"6\" | Legolas\n| rowspan=\"7\" | Archive sound\n|-\n| 2003\n| ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King (video game)|The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King]]''\n|-\n| 2004\n| ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Third Age]]''\n|-\n| 2012\n| ''[[Lego The Lord of the Rings (video game)|Lego The Lord of the Rings]]''\n|-\n| 2014\n| ''[[Lego The Hobbit (video game)|Lego The Hobbit]]''\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Lego Dimensions]]''\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''Disney Magic Kingdoms''\n| Will Turner\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year !! Award !! Category !! Nominee !! Result\n|-\n| rowspan=\"7\"|2001\n| Phoenix Film Critics Society Awards\n| Best Cast\n| rowspan=\"6\"|''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring]]''\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Empire Awards]]\n| [[Empire Award for Best Newcomer|Best Debut]]\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[MTV Movie Awards]]\n| [[MTV Movie Award for Best Breakthrough Performance|Best Breakthrough Performance]]\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Saturn Awards]]\n| Face of the Future&nbsp;\u2013 Male\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Screen Actors Guild Awards]]\n| [[Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by a Cast in a Motion Picture|Outstanding Performance by a Cast in a Motion Picture]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Teen Choice Awards]]\n| Choice Breakout (Male)\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Phoenix Film Critics Society Awards\n| Best Cast\n| ''[[Black Hawk Down (film)|Black Hawk Down]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"|2002\n| [[Online Film Critics Society Awards]]\n| [[Online Film Critics Society Award for Best Cast|Best Cast]]\n| rowspan=\"4\"|''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers]]''\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Phoenix Film Critics Society Awards\n| Best Cast\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Screen Actors Guild Awards]]\n| Outstanding Performance by a Cast in a Motion Picture\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"11\"|2003\n| [[MTV Movie Awards]]\n| Best Trans-Atlantic Performance\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[Australian Film Institut